Lets see, Manaburn was overpowered, Direcharm was overpowered...so what.  Hell can you solo a lvl 65 Mob as a Mage?  NO!!  But a enchanter can,,,is that overpowered?  Hell even clerics can solo a little better then us 61+.  Lets not forget about Wiz, Druid, Necro, Bard,,,etc.<br>
<br>
So tell me, why would this skill with the same DPS for 60 sec over power Magicians when so much have been taking away?<br>
<br>
One more thing, our pets are green and Shamans have higher level pets...which could make a difference on higher level mobs.  Have you thought about that?<br>
<br>
